divs: Sighting DetailsOn this early morning drive we noticed a particular cloud formation not usually seen, and we were in awe of the big circular formation cloud in the lower right hand of the picture. (It looked more beautiful than the picture shows)... I asked my front seat passenger to take pictures of the cloud as I was driving (she focused on the circular formation cloud on the lower right side of the picture). When I downloaded all of my pictures today from my camera to my laptop and casually looked through them, I am uncertain as to just what was to the right of a plane captured in the left hand side of the picture? This object is not in the other pictures she took so it can not be from the window... I have the other pictures if you want to see them... Just wanted to share and see if anyone else wanted to take a more in depth look...
Summary: Taking pictures of just clouds and did not see this unknown object flying near plane until downloaded to computer.
